Package: com.tlsfix
Name: TLSFix
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Modern HTTPS for legacy iOS. Routes HTTPS through a bundled mbedTLS (TLS 1.2/1.3) Secure Transport shim so old Safari and apps reach modern servers again. Safari is on by default. For the in-Settings configuration UI (per-app toggles and options) install PreferenceLoader and AppList too; otherwise enable apps by editing /var/mobile/Library/Preferences/com.tlsfix.plist by hand.
Depends: mobilesubstrate
Recommends: preferenceloader, applist
